def graph(item):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 10))
    plt.scatter(range(df.shape[0]), df[item].values, alpha = .2)
    plt.title(item)
    plt.xlabel(item)
    plt.ylabel("Clients Amount");
    plt.show()
